 ventually) dissolved by reline.  Over\n  time\, the parent 20 wt% PEC has 
 a liquid portion separate:\n  syneresis?\n• Giovanni prepared new PEC (20 
 wt%) 1:1.\n• now need to verify previous semester results with TMAO:urea a
 nd 1.3M\n  NaCl (7% saline).  Include reline with this cohort.\n• ☐ read p
 apers using NMR to characterize PECs before meeting with\n  Weiguo.
